info.title: Bad Case Of Loving You (Doctor, Doctor)

lines.text: a hot summer night,
fell like a net
i've gotta find my baby yet
i need you
to soothe my head,
turn my blue heart to red
doctor, doctor, give me the news
i've got a bad case of lovin' you
no pills' gonna cure my ill
i gotta bad case of lovin' you
a pretty face, don't make a pretty heart
i learned that, buddy from the start
i think i'm cute,
a little bit shy
momma, i ain't that kind of guy
doctor, doctor, give me the news
i've got a bad case of lovin' you
no pills' gonna cure my ill
i gotta bad case of lovin' you
i know, you like it,
you like it on top
tell me momma
are you gonna stop
you had me down,
twenty-one zip
smile of judas on your lip
shake my fist,
knock on wood,
i got it bad
and i've got it good
doctor, doctor, give me the news
i've got a bad case of lovin' you
no pills' gonna cure my ill
i gotta bad case of lovin' you
